### Submit a Form
POST http://localhost:8080/submission
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "form_id": 1,
  "answers": [
    {
      "question_id": 1,
      "answer": "John Doe",
      "answer_json": null
    },
    {
      "question_id": 2,
      "answer": "john.doe@example.com",
      "answer_json": null
    },
    {
      "question_id": 3,
      "answer": "1234567890",
      "answer_json": null
    },
    {
      "question_id": 4,
      "answer": "",
      "answer_json": {
        "selected_options": ["option1", "option2"],
        "other": "Custom option"
      }
    }
  ]
}

### Get Submission by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/submission/1
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Submissions by Form ID
GET http://localhost:8080/submission/form/1
Content-Type: application/json

### Submit a Form with JSON Answer
POST http://localhost:8080/submission
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "form_id": 1,
  "answers": [
    {
      "question_id": 5,
      "answer": "",
      "answer_json": {
        "rating": 5,
        "feedback": "Great service!",
        "recommend": true
      }
    }
  ]
}

